description.desc: [Master Level : 20]\n Gains resistance against all Magic attacks (Fire, Cold, Lightning & Poison.)
description.name: Elemental Resistance

description.desc: [Master Level : 30]\nAttacks multiple monsters serveral times by thrusting the spear.
description.name: Spear Crusher

description.desc: [Master Level : 30]\nAttacks multiple monsters serveral times by thrusting the pole arm.
description.name: Pole Arm Crusher

description.desc: [Master Level : 30]\n Attacks up to 6 monsters nearby in relatively distant range by swinging the Spear.
description.name: Dragon Fury: Spear

description.desc: [Master Level : 30]\n Attacks up to 6 monsters nearby in relatively distant range by swinging the pole arm.
description.name: Dragon Fury: Pole Arm

description.desc: [Master Level: 30]\n Attacks a single monster while disabling the monster's defending capacity. However, some damage will be done to the attacker him/herself.
description.name: Sacrifice

description.desc: [Master Level : 30]\n Attacks up to 15 monsters at once by temporarily stunning them.  It works only when more than 50% of HP is left.\nRequired Skill : #cAt least Level 3 on Sacrifice#
description.name: Dragon Roar

description.desc: [Master Level : 20]\n Nullifies "power-up" skills of multiple monsters with a given success rate.\nRequired Skill : #cAt least Level 3 on Dragon Blood#
description.name: Power Crash

description.desc: [Master Level : 20]\nIncreases the attacking capacity, but decreases HP steadily until 4 seconds before the remaining HP exhausts.
description.name: Dragon Blood
